ent for Keshari Residency, one of three affordable housing projects under PM Awas Yojana in the city. The project, a public-private partnership, will eventually comprise 1,300 dwelling units.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/bhubaneswar-hands-over-100-flats-in-third-phase-of-shantipalli-awas-yojana/125046914?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-130996/125046914.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}